metadata.name: Back to where it all started
metadata.description:
Sometimes on the way to a better life, you look for more power, wealth, or people to stick with; and in every experience, you lose a part of your inner peace. All the ups and downs, losses and sacrifices may eventually lead to one true state of freedom. Sometimes you’ll find peace right where you’d started your journey.

Adapted from “Peaky Blinders” TV series created by Steven Knight (2013-2022)

Edition 1/1
7500*10000px

Technique:
3d modeling, 2d exporting, digital collage making, manual image enhancement with color and lightness correction using Photoshop and Procreate
